---
model: vertexai/gemini-2.0-flash          # fast, cheap model is fine for extraction
format: json                              # we want pure JSON back
schema:                                   # expected output = array of QA objects
  type: array
  items:
    type: object
    properties:
      question: { type: string }
      answer:   { type: string }
    required: [question, answer]
input:                                    # the flow passes only one variable
  schema:
    text: string
---

From the text below, extract every QUESTION / ANSWER pair and return JSON
that matches the schema above.

TEXT:
{{text}}
